{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "爱如流星 各自的承诺",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "伊莉雅和莫尔提斯、\\n奈文和拉米艾尔两组人相遇。\\n就炼狱文书和少年一事，双方都不肯让步。\\n为了遵守各自的承诺，\\n双方最终只得全力交手。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯，你跟上来了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "嗯。不过这块板可真厉害啊。\\n是循着龙的魔力前进的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没错！这可是能感知魔力的方向\\n并为我们指路的雪地滑行板……\\n我叫它滑雪板！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "人类和龙的魔力\\n有各自不同的特征。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "用这个发明追踪那个天使的魔力，\\n好排除危险因素。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "比起寻找下落不明的少年，\\n这个方法更加可靠。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "等排除了危险因素，\\n我们也就能够放心地寻找少年。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没错！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "梅奈绝对不会希望看到\\n炼狱文书引起纷争。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "她肯定不是为了那种目的\\n才留下炼狱文书。所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我决不会把炼狱文书交给\\n企图用它来争夺权利的教会！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "啊！伊莉雅，看那边！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "找到了！我们上，莫尔提斯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "他们来了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "还是晚了一步吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "奈文，你小心一点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "那个男性就是在镇上与我擦肩而过的\\n拥有一股异样魔力的家伙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "似乎不容小觑啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我们要保护那个少年，\\n能把他交给我们吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "你们如何证明你们不会加害于他？\\n没法证明吧？所以我不会交给你们的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是那孩子的母亲拜托我们的。\\n我不会骗你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "那就由我们带他去他母亲的身边吧。\\n快告诉我他母亲在哪里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我不能告诉你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "因为……不能让我们知道他的母亲，\\n也就是炼狱之匙的主人在哪儿对吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "看来你们的目的也和我们一样……\\n都是为了炼狱文书啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你的理解能力很强嘛。\\n不愧是北部教会的“使徒”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "没想到能看穿我们的身份。\\n你们的本领也不小嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "过奖了。所以你打算怎么办？\\n我们就这样一直聊下去吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "这样聊下去也解决不了问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "确实。\\n看来……只能来硬的了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "奈文，这里交给我。\\n你保护好阿尔夫。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "看那神秘的板子，还有那巨大的魔力。\\n现在不知道他们有什么后手，\\n还是由身为龙的我来应战比较好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "而且在场的人里，\\n阿尔夫最信任的是你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "而且你不是向他承诺过吗？\\n现在就在他身边好好保护他吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "好吧……那就交给你了，拉米艾尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "嗯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "保护孩子可是父亲的责任。\\n来吧，让我来对付你们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}